{"tid":2358701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"帶你看世界／上海寫字樓空置率高 部分區域達40％","createTime":"2021-01-08T10:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T09:29:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d99c281a837fe368ab069743a99d585887c58a","tid":2358701,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"帶你看世界／上海寫字樓空置率高 部分區域達40％<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/11038/5120506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F11038%2F5120506&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=38fadcae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/11038/5120506</a><br />\n<br />\n上海寫字樓空置率高 部分區域達40％<br />\n受疫情影響，大陸一線城市辦公樓和商鋪整體承壓，空置率上升和租金下滑成為市場趨勢。資料顯示，今年第三季度，上海市優質辦公樓空置率為20.4％，相比第二季度增長了0.5個百分點，部分區域例如前灘和大虹橋更是空置率將近40％，分析師認為需求端的恢復速度沒有整體供給上漲來的快，明年可能會有比較明顯的反彈。"},{"pid":"5ae6715ffea217e18531879b8692b60da6c3dc3d","tid":2358701,"uid":292497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9624411be79728caa3e74a79722b91fe5162a5","tid":2358701,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"造謠"},{"pid":"996948932df78c37b0e72086e5618e8d7ec7ef4f","tid":2358701,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056080a4ea002070e8eb5901e35a03254dca329e","tid":2358701,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi